{
  "stem": "23410.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, after so many months, we have a certain relation.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And to take out and give them the hand, and say, here it is.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You don't know if [? he'd ?] [? run in ?] [? and ?] [? kill ?] [? it. ?] And he will open to door to take it, and we will hit him over the head and run out, and finish.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we did it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All of us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was one to speak to-- because I was inside.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had-- I could-- they-- they trusted that I could take it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It wasn't that I was smart or not, but I could.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I used to bring-- not the only this, by this time, November, I used to bring out for them wood to make fires, that they can keep warm in the night.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "By 10, 11 o'clock in Poland, it's quite cold.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It is not [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the Indian Summer.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So you say-- so you say, I will-- you take a lot of wood, and you have something in the hand, and said, I want to come out now.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so-- but I was inside, and I was a guy that did for them for fire.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One way or another, they ask me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It wasn't-- So you had the opportunity.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You were able--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I did not know anybody.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I did not know even where to go.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I did-- You know, as I told you the other day, like they [? decide ?] that I'm [? a leader. ?] I did not even know where I am in Lemburg.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's like dropping somebody off in the middle of New York.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Where am I?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "How do you go to this street?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "How do you go?",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
